•
Volume Score (25%): $1M+ volume = 100 pts, tracks momentum
•
Liquidity Score (25%): $100K+ liquidity = 80 pts, measures stability
•
Price Momentum (25%): >100% gain 24h = 80 pts, detects pumps
•
Market Cap (15%): $100K-$1M sweet spot = 100 pts, ideal entry
•
Age Score (10%): <1 hour old = 100 pts, catches earliest stage

Social Metrics (30% weight):
•
Twitter mentions increasing = bullish signal
•
Telegram activity surge = community engagement
•
Verified accounts = legitimacy indicator
•
Engagement rate = real vs bot activity
Hype Score 70+ = Strong bullish signals matching historical 10x+ tokens

Hype Score 50-69 = Moderate potential, worth monitoring

Hype Score <50 = Filtered out, too risky
